posts.cooked:
Our robot weighs just over 75 lbs (with battery!) and is pretty much fully assembled at this point an advantage of making the whole thing out of bamboo and thin-walled aluminium I guess!

Were for sure going to need to add some kind of weighting to the bottom though Any suggestions besides a steel baseplate lol?
